Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We are scheduled for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the first break will be at 2 to 11.30.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, in the universal room, which is the last room to the left over here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there is refreshments for you on both breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the lunch hour will be from 12 to 2 o'clock
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you can leave if you want to have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:04:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then after the second break is at 3.15,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's when we have our question and answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you have any questions that you would like to ask Dr. at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll form two lines and we'll sign books at that time also
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can come up and ask any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the good news is that we have a new website that's ready to be up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert's been working on it diligently for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you'd like to take a peek at it, it's Dr. Paul Kempf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.info.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like to take a quick peek at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have little clips of some of the seminars in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.info.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.info.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like to take a peek, we're going to have some little cuts out of seminars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean I'm, does that qualify me as a blogger?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that make me a blogger?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You are. You are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to be blogged, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You ain't seen no blogging until you see my blogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's humility for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a divine blessing to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what we're talking about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I made a diagram.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we all start off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The same way that we start off in the end of the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And to save all that time of having to listen through all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You live your life in a contemplative style.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In a contemplative style, you're not commenting on everything all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not taking a positionality about it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just witnessing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The witness is already detached from the participant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the leading edge of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not content with just witnessing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And give you its opinion, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the world going to do without?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A contemplative lifestyle, if you do it habitually,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it will come out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The witnessing that all phenomena are occurring spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As a consequence of that which they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And for no other reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that things are emerging, evolving, and appearing as they appear spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,By contemplation and witnessing then, you've shut off the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And without the mind, you don't see any cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mentalization you project.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if through humility, you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, I don't know what anything means anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to be the witness of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you witness creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:08:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you witness creation, doing whatever creation is, how it's evolving at this unfoldingness over what the world calls time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sequentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize that all phenomena are being what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Expressing their essence by which what the world calls evolution occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, it throws it on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out of nowhere, not out of thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That creation and evolution are the one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That what you're seeing is evolution, which is creation in 3D.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The linear expression of evolution then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The linear which you can witness in the physical domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody have a problem with evolution and creation are one and the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, there's no conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, non-duality means you withdraw from the participant experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Experience or edge of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead, you withdraw to the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You withdraw from thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinkingness comes to your aid when you want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to be at the effect of thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That it allows you peace when it wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You think when you decide to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When there's some purpose or benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that you have to go into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And left brain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sequentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is wearisome, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why anybody prizes the body and the mind is beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But they do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Both are wearisome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,However, without a body you can't walk around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can see it does serve a useful purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about overcoming obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the name of the.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I seldom pay attention to the title of the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did notice it was overcoming obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Overcoming obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the human condition is certainly full of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Buddha said transcend the identification of the linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this is a world of considerable discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Which we witness in today's news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The tragic events which sweep across the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In one place or another almost continuously throughout all of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Flood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunamis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurricanes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Same time they're exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the same time they allow us the full expression of our own karmic potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We always watch the weather news at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The storm stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Storm stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And we notice that the survivors of catastrophes in relating it subsequently almost all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:12:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost every single one of them remarked about how they prayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, one of the quickest ways to God is to face sudden death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Atheism goes just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's possible through surrender to face anything with great equanimity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk right into the hail of bullets and either you die or you don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is surrender to the will of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is different than nihilism.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different than denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different than skepticism let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I thought today also the obstacles are the limitations of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And skepticism has sort of showed up on the radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I thought we have a similar goal in mind with skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Skepticism arose in ancient Greece.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The philosophy of ancient Greece.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The followers of Pyro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,P-R-R-Y-H-O I think is the spelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Skeptikos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Greek word is skeptikos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the philosophy of the skeptic was that truth is not knowable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is not knowable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is exactly what we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind in and of itself is unable to discern truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you would think skepticism would be a great fan of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it seems to be antagonized by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mainly because, you know, consciousness research verifies the validity of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, which is antagonistic to the skeptic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, of course, the problem with the skeptic is if truth is unknowable,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it means that there is no value to their speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because their speech is also there expressing ignorance, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the skeptic is hung in his own petard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If knowledge is not knowable, then what are they blabbering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we did write a little essay on skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that sort of has come up in the world of bloggers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I am now a fellow blogger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they better watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffer from bloggerism.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Much of bloggerism, you know, is services.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It provides information, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's what I call the vanity sites, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill's corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill tells you what he thinks about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, skepticism calibrates about 160.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a low.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In as much as ostensibly, it supposedly is seeking the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it is very close to nihilism.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nihilism calibrates at 120.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It is also very close to anarchy because it denies the authenticity of all authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore skepticism is by its nature atheistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't carry it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The good side of skepticism is that it has revealed outrageous frauds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Outrageous frauds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore I'm an enthusiast to skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, with a sharp eye on its downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when you study skepticism, you end up skeptical of scepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not think that skepticism is going to lead us to God or to truth or the salvation of mankind, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, every new development in mankind's history brings the skeptics out of the woodwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a little worried that they weren't coming around after I published truth versus nihilism.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, good God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even worth the skeptics attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But now my ego is reinflated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I am happy to be under attack by the skeptics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So now I'm somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have my sympathy is with what I think is their ostensible purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an somebody, I'm not somebody, I have a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the methodology, etc., it doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like the message, you attack the messengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So also in blogger land we've had ad hominem attacks on yours truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank thee, Lord, that I do not have an unpaid parking ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean as the whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No parking tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,confrontational. There's a caveat in the front of the book, Truth vs. Fault. The caveat tells you that it's confrontational.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not prepared for it, don't read any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people ignored the caveat, obviously. I thought we would do some, a couple of things, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the other thing they question, of course, is kinesiology. So I said before I wrote this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll get politically motivated attacks, which they all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:18:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you'll get people that are very anti-God, they all are, and then you get the critics of kinesiology, because
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,not a single
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,critic has addressed the main premises or the main conclusions or anything important in the book, so they didn't comprehend that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So nobody has addressed that at all. They only go for the peripheral issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So the skeptic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, questions kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I taught kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, kinesiology was new on the radar 30 years ago. It's old hat now. Everybody's
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,done all the tricks to try and prove it and disprove it, and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,there's many very excellent
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,DVDs out there by professionals in kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,who know a great deal about it. I know practically nothing about it. I just know yes or no, that's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's many tricks you can do. You can go like this, and they go weak, and then you go like this, and they go hot,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you go like this, and they go strong, and you go this, and they go weak, so
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes me dizzy, and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat Flanagan used to be an expert showing on that, and so if you're really interested in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm only interested in it that it serves a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,pedagogical function
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because it allows us how to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,move from the Newtonian paradigm of science
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,into the nonlinear domain. It gives us the only trail I know of from the linear to the nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I thought it served a pedagogical technique, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But if your findings come up to support what people don't want to hear about, then they suddenly hate kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the only other possible attack they can have on it, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I used to give lectures all over the country, all the world in fact, and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, the results were consistent in every single country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The mistake I made in meoculpa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the error, the omission, was in power versus force. You know, I'll tell you how it developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw kinesiology with John Diamond and did a workshop with him, and then I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,started giving lectures on it because I had a huge clinic, you see, and we used holistic
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,practices. We thought kinesiology would lead us maybe to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,unsuspected causes of mental disorders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I added that to, you know, we did all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They were non-traditional and had tremendous recoveries in hopeless cases. The clinic specialized in hopeless cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We had the largest practice in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,People came from all over the world because we've got recoveries where nobody else could, and it's because we weren't just limited to the Newtonian
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,traditional science.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,medicine has always been town versus gown. The town
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,are the doctors that are out there, and the gown
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is the academics, who live in a much more restrained
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,world of provability.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The experienced clinician can get recoveries where the academics can't, so our usual patient
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,had been to all the universities, seen all the specialists, and were given up as hopeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we specialized in the hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So we looked for everything that could be helpful on kinesiology was one of the things we researched.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I began teaching it. So
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,when we started teaching it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to give a class.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the clinic back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we had A Course in Miracles students
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I grabbed a couple of people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there's one traditional test.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take an ordinary person
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and they look at fluorescent lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,they go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hold sweet and low
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where there's solar plexus,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So I grabbed a couple of people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said, okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:21:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,well, let's try this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So we did the fluorescent thing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and they didn't go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we tried the sweet and low,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,they didn't go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, God,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they're going to make
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,lousy test subjects, I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But the curiosity was,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,how come they didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it had something to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,with A Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So we got some new students
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,who were just starting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A Course in Miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I tested them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They went weak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,with fluorescent lights
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and sweet and low.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And we tested them serially.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And about the time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.69,0:22:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,they got to less than 75,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,80 around in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly fluorescent lights
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,did not make them go weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,nor did sweet and low
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,nor any other local stimulus
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,make them go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,when I wrote Power Versus Force
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and we did a video on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the video is still,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.75,0:22:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't there one,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.48,0:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a demonstration of Power Versus Force
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,on kinesiology?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:22:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all the people I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and hung out with
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,all calibrated over,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,200, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So we thought that kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.89,0:23:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,would be useful for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we later discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can't use it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.84,0:23:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of the question
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,also has to be 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I didn't put that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in Power Versus Force
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and I must have created
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the illusion that anybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.58,0:23:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,anywhere can do it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,under any circumstance,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's later corrected
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.41,0:23:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in subsequent books.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But so I take responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that we did not know it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we did the video
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,on Power Versus Force
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,demonstrating the kinesiologic test,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.50,0:23:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we grabbed everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that came along
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and they were all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So of course it worked
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for 100% of those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it probably worked
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,for 100% of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.93,0:23:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in this crowd, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because you wouldn't be here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,if you were under 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.58,0:23:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:23:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So the error was
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought everybody could do it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and I misled the public
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,by, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,by, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,omission.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.98,0:24:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness research,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,are evolving,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.27,0:24:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.83,0:24:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.07,0:24:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought we'd do
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a brief demonstration
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.81,0:24:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.44,0:24:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for those of you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.38,0:24:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who never heard
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.22,0:24:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,one of my wonderful lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,on kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do the whole thing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.68,0:24:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in about two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.20,0:24:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll take two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.64,0:24:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.78,0:24:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.15,0:24:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Under threat, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.97,0:24:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.19,0:24:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a calcitrant lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.36,0:24:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.04,0:24:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.52,0:24:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.67,0:24:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.06,0:24:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if the crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.89,0:24:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,can see this or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.04,0:24:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.25,0:24:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
