Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.93,0:33:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.27,0:34:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The narcissistic ego, uh, feels extremely threatened that there is such a thing as absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.80,0:34:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,truth, uh, and divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.11,0:34:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the narcissistic ego, uh, to itself is divinity, and therefore God would be the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.71,0:34:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,ultimate hated rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.23,0:34:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see, therefore, the criticisms are, uh, pretty polemic, pretty polemic, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.46,0:34:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it threatens the, it threatens the narcissistic ego, uh, so, see if a person's
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.67,0:34:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,really interested in inquiry, they ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.55,0:34:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.55,0:34:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.94,0:34:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.94,0:34:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.32,0:34:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How come this or that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.65,0:34:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, most, a lot of the questions are, you know, have to do with the irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.65,0:34:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How come a hippopotamus calibrates more than a toad or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.71,0:34:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Having nothing to do with getting to God, but, uh, you know, the design of the books
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.96,0:35:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,has the intention of enlightenment, so it's only to, to provide some kind of a, uh, teaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.57,0:35:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, technique, method that just confirms God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.32,0:35:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.32,0:35:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That just confirms, gives an additional confirm...confirmation, because of the modern mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.65,0:35:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The, uh, in ancient times, uh, science did not dominate, nor did Newtonian paradigm of,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.71,0:35:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, provability and causability, so in the old days faith was all that was, uh, sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.15,0:35:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.15,0:35:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The modern mind, uh, takes faith, but with a grain of salt, so the idea of kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.28,0:35:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,as a pedagogical technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.28,0:35:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is it adds an affirmation to truth that is comprehensible and meaningful
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.82,0:35:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to the modern intellectual scientific mind, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.46,0:35:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's just a pedagogical technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.40,0:35:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I pointed out in my response to that blogger, give him a blog, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.82,0:36:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,These are not textbooks on kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.67,0:36:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, pick up John Diamond or somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.94,0:36:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, I just thought I'd mention that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.86,0:36:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I mentioned it was because somebody sent me a book on bloggers,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.92,0:36:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and it said the first negative blog that comes up about you, you better answer it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.23,0:36:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise it's going to be copied all over the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.15,0:36:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So ordinarily I would have just ignored it and let it go away by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.90,0:36:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I decided it's better to do what we've got to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.53,0:36:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.32,0:36:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,misunderstanding of spirituality that thinks it has to do with passivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.05,0:36:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Passivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.73,0:36:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people think you should be of a certain political persuasion
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.84,0:36:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and also a pacifist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.17,0:36:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Passivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.07,0:36:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As we pointed out, truth versus falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.46,0:37:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Passivity actually calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.40,0:37:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, spiritual truth means to stand for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.86,0:37:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To stand for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.80,0:37:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Passivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.44,0:37:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Passivity, then, is encouraging fallacy, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.82,0:37:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To not speak back to falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.98,0:37:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To not stand up for truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.13,0:37:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We noticed that standing up for truth cost Socrates his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.82,0:37:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It cost Jesus Christ his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.44,0:37:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It cost all the apostles.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.80,0:37:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All the apostles ended up in disasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.44,0:37:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Any one of them could have survived by merely refuting
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.44,0:37:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.07,0:37:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Refuting the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.07,0:37:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.44,0:37:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stand for the truth and I think the best way to do it is to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.32,0:37:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.15,0:37:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore I wrote an essay on skepticism and I wrote an essay on kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.73,0:37:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,which will be out there in bloggerland maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.98,0:38:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just that because you want to recontextualize it so that it's more comprehensible and then
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.65,0:38:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,what they do about it is their own karmic problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.44,0:38:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so is there any more questions about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.65,0:38:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There was also a misquote.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.59,0:38:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't mind misquoting you all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.09,0:38:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That I lost my thumb in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.34,0:38:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not lose my thumb in an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.84,0:38:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,nor did I state that I,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.17,0:38:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I never stated that I lost my thumb in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.71,0:38:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I said in the universe, no accident is possible
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.84,0:38:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because everything is in divine order.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.94,0:38:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe is infinite, infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.78,0:38:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can anything occur outside of the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.17,0:38:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is in divine order.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.03,0:38:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long ago, four of us met,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.84,0:38:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think in the northwest someplace at a convention,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.15,0:38:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,four of us of this group,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.94,0:39:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,all four of us are missing a thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.76,0:39:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, there's another missing thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.42,0:39:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Four of us missing thumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.48,0:39:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that's by accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.96,0:39:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have four of us that show up at the same place
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.90,0:39:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,all missing the same thumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.28,0:39:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You notice in my writings I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.50,0:39:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,swear no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.01,0:39:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Swear no oaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.88,0:39:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Or let the words be my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.75,0:39:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, it came out of the Bible,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.76,0:39:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,swearing oaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.76,0:39:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know where it came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.82,0:39:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.42,0:39:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Swear no oaths because you don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.38,0:39:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in what lifetime you're going to pay it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.65,0:39:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So all four of us paid it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.11,0:39:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We were members 300 years ago in the same brotherhood
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.67,0:39:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and we all swore and did the blood thumb deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.55,0:39:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.82,0:39:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,if we break this vow,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.34,0:39:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,may so and so happen to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.96,0:39:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.11,0:39:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was not by accident at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.96,0:39:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.75,0:40:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and when all four of us came together,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.61,0:40:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.01,0:40:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we did some past life research.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.78,0:40:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We all belonged to the same organization
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.01,0:40:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and the same group.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.51,0:40:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And we all left it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.05,0:40:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and may the reverse be our fate
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.17,0:40:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,was the price we paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.51,0:40:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So losing the thumb,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.76,0:40:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,was not accidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.51,0:40:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's confusing it with intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.51,0:40:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think it's not intentional,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.51,0:40:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't mean it's accidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.51,0:40:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means it's not intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.51,0:40:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So losing the thumb was not intentional consciously,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.51,0:40:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but fate just had its moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.51,0:40:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom, like that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.51,0:40:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Quicker than a wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.51,0:40:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Quicker than a wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.51,0:40:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you only need this one to hitchhike,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.51,0:40:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.51,0:40:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.26,0:40:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hitchhiked to school every day for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.26,0:40:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,out in the cold and snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.26,0:40:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wisconsin.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.88,0:40:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course then I was also maligned
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.88,0:40:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was one commentary,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.88,0:40:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I'll finish with the Bloggerland.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.88,0:40:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It said,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.38,0:41:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.38,0:41:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,he grew up in the Midwest
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.88,0:41:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and was in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.38,0:41:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.55,0:41:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.80,0:41:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He grew up in the Midwest
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.80,0:41:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and was in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.80,0:41:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And went to church as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.30,0:41:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.30,0:41:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what can you expect from a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.44,0:41:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought I'd share those little biographical things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.44,0:41:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we live in a current world
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.44,0:41:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in which Bloggerland is a reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.44,0:41:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore it's just something
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.44,0:41:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we have learned to live with, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.44,0:41:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to work a computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.44,0:41:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.69,0:41:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I once came across the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.69,0:41:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was covering a clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.69,0:41:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in Cottonwood
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.69,0:41:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,where the doctor was sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.69,0:41:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and they gave me this office.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.69,0:41:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This was many years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.69,0:41:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and here sat this thing I'd heard about
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.69,0:41:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,called the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.69,0:41:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I examined it all over,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.69,0:41:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and I looked at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.69,0:41:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't find an on or off switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.51,0:42:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.51,0:42:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I examined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.51,0:42:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no on or off switch on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.61,0:42:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The next week I came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.61,0:42:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,same office.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.61,0:42:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I examined it all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.61,0:42:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no on or off switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.90,0:42:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the end of my interest in computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.03,0:42:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the end of my romance with computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.03,0:42:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.03,0:42:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.36,0:42:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,how many people here are new, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.78,0:42:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.78,0:42:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.78,0:42:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We do this again,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.78,0:42:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because for the sake of the new,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.78,0:42:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to cover the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.78,0:42:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The basics are in the written material.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.78,0:42:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.78,0:42:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't spend a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.78,0:42:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But we do cover the basics enough
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.78,0:42:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,for somebody who hasn't been here before
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.78,0:42:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or is a guest
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.78,0:42:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to give them some comprehension
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.78,0:42:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and overall contextualization, Betty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.96,0:42:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Betty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.96,0:42:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Boop.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.96,0:42:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Way ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.51,0:42:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.51,0:42:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.78,0:42:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the other thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.78,0:43:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,people accuse you of positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.78,0:43:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because they're so positionalized,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.78,0:43:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't imagine that somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.78,0:43:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,could not come from a non-positionality
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.78,0:43:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for some kind of gain, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.78,0:43:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They project onto you what they do themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.78,0:43:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that you don't have any stake
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.80,0:43:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in what the answer's going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.80,0:43:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So to get a correct answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.80,0:43:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't have any stake in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.80,0:43:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I'll say,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.80,0:43:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,first of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.80,0:43:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,ask for the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.80,0:43:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.80,0:43:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Number one, get permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.03,0:43:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.15,0:43:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.15,0:43:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in some of the lectures,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.15,0:43:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we got nos, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.15,0:43:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We got nos.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.15,0:43:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.15,0:43:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because of people that were in the group,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.15,0:43:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we got the no at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.15,0:43:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.15,0:43:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you can get a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.15,0:43:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you have to position
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.15,0:43:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what you want to address
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.15,0:43:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,as a statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.15,0:43:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,not a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.15,0:43:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.15,0:43:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Rover is still
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.23,0:43:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,something or other.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.28,0:44:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you quickly press down,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.40,0:44:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's a very quick response.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.40,0:44:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask for the,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.40,0:44:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.40,0:44:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So the right way to do it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.40,0:44:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.40,0:44:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.48,0:44:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the highest good,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.48,0:44:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to calibrate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.48,0:44:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.48,0:44:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And so and so calibrates over 200, 300, 400,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.48,0:44:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever, until the arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.48,0:44:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you have no vested interest
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.48,0:44:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in that answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.48,0:44:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,having turned it over
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.48,0:44:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to the highest good,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.53,0:44:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and avoiding, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.73,0:44:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to beg the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.73,0:44:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So people who are integrous
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.01,0:44:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and who follow the right technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.01,0:44:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,then again,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.01,0:44:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a matter of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.03,0:44:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, kinesiology is not the only way
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.03,0:44:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to discern truth from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.03,0:44:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,physiologically.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.13,0:44:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a whole raft of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.59,0:44:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole raft of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.59,0:44:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pupillary response,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.59,0:44:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,blood pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.59,0:44:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.59,0:45:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,vasomotor response,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.59,0:45:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,idiomotor response,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.59,0:45:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,acupuncture balance,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.59,0:45:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,brain physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.59,0:45:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a million ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.59,0:45:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are very good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.59,0:45:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They just stand up,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.59,0:45:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and truth makes them fall forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.59,0:45:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and falsehood makes them fall backward.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.59,0:45:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use your whole body like a pendulum.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.59,0:45:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, dowsers do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.80,0:45:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember going across the border
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.80,0:45:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,into Northern Ireland
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.80,0:45:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,many years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.80,0:45:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,when there was conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.90,0:45:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you crossed the border
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.90,0:45:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,into Northern Ireland,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.90,0:45:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the police there patted you down,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.90,0:45:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and they looked you in the eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.90,0:45:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,closely at your pupil,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.90,0:45:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and they said,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.90,0:45:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,are you carrying a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.90,0:45:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They watched your pupil response.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.03,0:45:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, being a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.03,0:45:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.03,0:45:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're watching the pupil?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.03,0:45:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.03,0:45:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch for a flare of the pupil
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.09,0:45:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when the guy lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.09,0:45:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.09,0:45:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the lie detector is set up
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.09,0:45:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to do all these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.09,0:45:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Body language,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.09,0:46:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,facial expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.09,0:46:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,voice analysis is common.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.09,0:46:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy gives a lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.09,0:46:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and the voice analyst says
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.09,0:46:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,he was lying on this sentence,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.09,0:46:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,he was lying on this sentence,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.09,0:46:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,lying on this sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.09,0:46:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's many ways to verify it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.09,0:46:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinesiology is so quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.09,0:46:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I just say,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.09,0:46:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think about,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.09,0:46:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so-and-so has a good idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.09,0:46:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.09,0:46:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes less than about 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.09,0:46:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I can't set up
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.09,0:46:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole brainwave machine
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.09,0:46:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and do all that crazy stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.09,0:46:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for a voice analysis machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.09,0:46:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, kinesiology is not,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.09,0:46:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.09,0:46:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just one of many,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.09,0:46:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.09,0:46:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.09,0:46:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I thought I'd mention that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.09,0:46:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.57,0:46:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll go back
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.57,0:46:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to the map of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.57,0:46:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,which is pretty much known worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.57,0:46:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in just about every language
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.57,0:46:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.57,0:46:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.61,0:46:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we use kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.61,0:46:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop a war, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.80,0:46:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.80,0:46:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a near ballistic missile war,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.80,0:46:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the verge of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.80,0:47:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.80,0:47:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.90,0:47:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan and I got
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.90,0:47:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,tracked halfway across the globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.90,0:47:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.90,0:47:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with all the top officials
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.90,0:47:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of the government
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.90,0:47:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of all the officials,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.90,0:47:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,who are very wise men,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.90,0:47:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,thank God,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.90,0:47:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we analyzed every single move
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.90,0:47:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,on this side
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.90,0:47:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and every single response
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.90,0:47:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.90,0:47:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And we came up
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.90,0:47:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with a resolution
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.90,0:47:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to support the person's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.90,0:47:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,political power,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.90,0:47:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in which case
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.90,0:47:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he will drop military power.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.90,0:47:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Within 72 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.28,0:47:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the headlines
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.28,0:47:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,were a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.28,0:47:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.28,0:47:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it's pragmatic value.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.28,0:47:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It allows you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.28,0:47:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to access information
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.28,0:47:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not available
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.28,0:47:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,by any ordinary means.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.28,0:47:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A great deal
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.28,0:47:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of the stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.36,0:47:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that we appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.36,0:47:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that appears
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.36,0:47:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in Truth Versus Falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.36,0:47:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we held back
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.36,0:47:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for several years.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.36,0:47:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.36,0:47:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we held back
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.36,0:47:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the publication.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.36,0:47:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.40,0:47:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.40,0:47:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the recent news,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.40,0:47:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we knew years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.40,0:47:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.40,0:47:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,food for oil
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.40,0:47:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.40,0:47:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew that years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.40,0:47:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.40,0:47:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it allows you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.40,0:47:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,access to information.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.50,0:47:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.50,0:47:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,not all the information
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.50,0:47:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,can you share
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.50,0:48:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.50,0:48:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.50,0:48:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.50,0:48:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a great deal
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.50,0:48:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we did not share
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.50,0:48:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.50,0:48:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.50,0:48:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it's bad enough
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.50,0:48:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in blogger land
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.50,0:48:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with what we did,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.59,0:48:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.59,0:48:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.59,0:48:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,say,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.59,0:48:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,tell everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.59,0:48:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.59,0:48:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.71,0:48:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.71,0:48:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.71,0:48:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.71,0:48:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,if the intention
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.71,0:48:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is integrous then,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.71,0:48:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,this serves
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.71,0:48:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,a very useful
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.71,0:48:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,pragmatic function.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.71,0:48:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.71,0:48:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the perennial philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.71,0:48:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Although,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.71,0:48:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it's actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.71,0:48:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.71,0:48:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.92,0:48:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,this is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.92,0:48:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the perennial
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.92,0:48:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,philosophy
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.92,0:48:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.80,0:48:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's most recent,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.80,0:48:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it was a psychologist
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.80,0:48:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,named,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.80,0:48:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,something,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.80,0:48:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,who published
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.80,0:48:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,an article
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.80,0:48:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,on it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.80,0:48:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,back in the 50s.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.80,0:48:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Columbia
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.80,0:48:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychoanalytic
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.80,0:48:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.94,0:48:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,where I,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.94,0:48:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,my analyst was.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.94,0:48:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.94,0:48:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,our training
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.94,0:48:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,analysts there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.94,0:48:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These are called
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.00,0:48:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.00,0:48:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychoanalytic
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.00,0:48:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.00,0:48:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These are called
