Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.03,0:53:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.03,0:53:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.25,0:53:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.25,0:53:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think
