Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.68,1:51:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.68,1:51:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,neediness then disappears
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.68,1:51:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so what do you want to do is
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.00,1:51:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,transcend identification with the experiencer
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.00,1:51:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that's one of the great
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.00,1:51:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the great obstacle
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.28,1:51:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you are not the
