Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.28,1:51:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you're experiencing
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.28,1:51:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing is happening on its own
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.15,1:51:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,all right
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.68,1:51:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so you got to tell the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.68,1:51:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,humility means to tell the truth
